defence-orange.description: Originating from Defence colours, this orange has been updated to pass WCAG, and work well with our other colours in the brand. This colour acts well particularly in UI as a purposefully eye catcher to helps navigate the user to their next step.

Navy.description: As the main colour of ServiceConnect, you will see this to be the most commonly used colour when it comes to application. This navy is a versatile colour, being able to be used with all other colours of the brand and passes WCAG.
